Disgusting?
"No, " says Eric Blanche, Director General Adapt, an organization that organizes a week of employment for disabled persons."
"In 15 years, significant progress has been made."
"At that time, the unemployment rate was not 2 but 3 times higher."
"One day there's still a lot of work ahead."
It must be said that there are still many obstacles to the employment of a disabled person.
